prodNameC: "代首林" 促腎上腺皮質賀爾蒙放射免疫分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Calibrator 0: lyophilized reagent, ACTH-free human plasma.
ACTH Calibrators (A-E): lyophilized reagent, ACTH calibrators (porcine), at nominal concentrations ranging from 20-500 pg/mL (4.5-112 picomoles/L).
ACTH Antiserum: lyophilized reagent, Rabbit anti-ACTH serum diluted in BSA-borate buffer with Thimerosal.
I-125 ACTH: lyophilized reagent, Synthetic ACTH labeled with iodine-125, diluted in BSA-borated-EDTA buffer with Thimerosal.
Precipitating Complex (GAR-PPT): lyophilized reagent, Normal rabbit serum, pre-precipitated with goat anti-rabbit serum and polyethylene glycol (PEG), is diluted in BSA-borate buffer with Thimerosal.
ACTH Control (Level 1 and 2): lyophilized reagent, Human plasma spiked, if necessary, with the appropriate amount of synthetic ACTH to obtain a concentrate within a specified range.
applicantName: 泰歷藥品儀器股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市大同區承德路二段81號15樓
efficacy: 藉由放射免疫法(RIA)用以檢測人體EDTA血漿檢體中促腎上腺皮質賀爾蒙(ACTH)之含量。
